### Get Profile Image via Images Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/images/some-uuid.webp
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get Pending Invites for User - Success
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/invites
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get Pending Invites for User - Unauthorized (no token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/invites

### Get Pending Invites for User - Forbidden (wrong user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/invites
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Get Pending Invites for User - Invalid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/invalid-uuid/invites
Authorization: {{authToken}}